{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":860,"text":"I've got a confession."},{"time":2580,"text":"I love looking through people's garbage."},{"time":5812,"text":"Now, it's not some creepy thing."},{"time":7741,"text":"I'm usually just looking\nfor old electronics,"},{"time":9931,"text":"stuff I can take to my workshop and hack."},{"time":12381,"text":"I do have a fetish for CD-ROM drives."},{"time":16044,"text":"Each one's got three different motors,"},{"time":18677,"text":"so now you can build things that move."},{"time":20638,"text":"There's switches so you can\nturn things on and off."},{"time":23377,"text":"There's even a freaking laser,"},{"time":25259,"text":"so you can make a cool robot\ninto an awesome robot."}]},{"cues":[{"time":30778,"text":"Now, I've built\na lot of stuff out of garbage,"},{"time":33968,"text":"and some of these things\nhave even been kind of useful."},{"time":36773,"text":"But here's the thing,"},{"time":37982,"text":"for me, garbage is just a chance to play,"},{"time":40607,"text":"to be creative and build things\nto amuse myself."},{"time":43554,"text":"This is what I love doing,\nso I just made it part of my day job."},{"time":47214,"text":"I lead a university-based\nbiological research lab,"},{"time":49795,"text":"where we value curiosity\nand exploration above all else."},{"time":53756,"text":"We aren't focused\non any particular problem,"},{"time":56376,"text":"and we're not trying to solve\nany particular disease."},{"time":58962,"text":"This is just a place where people can come"},{"time":61670,"text":"and ask fascinating questions\nand find answers."},{"time":65470,"text":"And I realized a long time ago"},{"time":67359,"text":"that if I challenge people\nto build the equipment they need"},{"time":70625,"text":"out of the garbage I find,"},{"time":72762,"text":"it's a great way to foster creativity."},{"time":75549,"text":"And what happened"},{"time":76724,"text":"was that artists and scientists\nfrom around the world"},{"time":79629,"text":"started coming to my lab."},{"time":81669,"text":"And it's not just because\nwe value unconventional ideas,"},{"time":84902,"text":"it's because we test and validate them"},{"time":87244,"text":"with scientific rigor."}]},{"cues":[{"time":89620,"text":"So one day I was hacking something,\nI was taking it apart,"},{"time":93545,"text":"and I had this sudden idea:"},{"time":95426,"text":"Could I treat biology like hardware?"},{"time":98889,"text":"Could I dismantle a biological system,"},{"time":101164,"text":"mix and match the parts"},{"time":102611,"text":"and then put it back together\nin some new and creative way?"},{"time":105946,"text":"My lab started working on this,"},{"time":108054,"text":"and I want to show you the result."}]},{"cues":[{"time":111601,"text":"Can any of you guys\ntell me what fruit this is?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":115278,"text":"Audience: Apple!"}]},{"cues":[{"time":116453,"text":"Andrew Pelling:\nThat's right -- it's an apple."},{"time":118634,"text":"Now, I actually want you to notice as well"},{"time":120657,"text":"that this is a lot redder\nthan most apples."},{"time":124294,"text":"And that's because\nwe grew human cells into it."},{"time":127044,"text":"We took a totally innocent\nMacintosh apple,"},{"time":131246,"text":"removed all the apple cells and DNA"},{"time":134289,"text":"and then implanted human cells."},{"time":136332,"text":"And what we're left with\nafter removing all the apple cells"},{"time":139405,"text":"is this cellulose scaffold."},{"time":141170,"text":"This is the stuff that gives plants\ntheir shape and texture."},{"time":144331,"text":"And these little holes that you can see,"},{"time":146327,"text":"this is where all\nthe apple cells used to be."},{"time":149254,"text":"So then we come along,"},{"time":150462,"text":"we implant some mammalian cells\nthat you can see in blue."},{"time":153548,"text":"What happens is,\nthese guys start multiplying"},{"time":155780,"text":"and they fill up this entire scaffold."}]},{"cues":[{"time":158414,"text":"As weird as this is,"},{"time":160775,"text":"it's actually really reminiscent\nof how our own tissues are organized."},{"time":164955,"text":"And we found in our pre-clinical work"},{"time":167232,"text":"that you can implant\nthese scaffolds into the body,"},{"time":169652,"text":"and the body will send in cells\nand a blood supply"},{"time":172359,"text":"and actually keep these things alive."},{"time":175348,"text":"This is the point\nwhen people started asking me,"},{"time":178469,"text":"\"Andrew, can you make\nbody parts out of apples?\""},{"time":183794,"text":"And I'm like, \"You've come\nto the right place.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":186049,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":187715,"text":"I actually brought this up with my wife."},{"time":189924,"text":"She's a musical instrument maker,"},{"time":191682,"text":"and she does a lot\nof wood carving for a living."},{"time":194529,"text":"So I asked her,"},{"time":196865,"text":"\"Could you, like,\nliterally carve some ears"},{"time":200126,"text":"out of an apple for us?\""},{"time":201682,"text":"And she did."},{"time":203157,"text":"So I took her ears to the lab."},{"time":205953,"text":"We then started preparing them."},{"time":208979,"text":"Yeah, I know."}]},{"cues":[{"time":210340,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":213397,"text":"It's a good lab, man."}]},{"cues":[{"time":215139,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":216624,"text":"And then we grew cells on them."},{"time":219008,"text":"And this is the result."}]},{"cues":[{"time":221916,"text":"Listen, my lab is not\nin the ear-manufacturing business."},{"time":227778,"text":"People have actually been working\non this for decades."},{"time":231138,"text":"Here's the issue:"},{"time":232810,"text":"commercial scaffolds can be\nreally expensive and problematic,"},{"time":237240,"text":"because they're sourced\nfrom proprietary products,"},{"time":239865,"text":"animals or cadavers."},{"time":247259,"text":"We used an apple and it cost pennies."}]},{"cues":[{"time":250873,"text":"What's also really cool here"},{"time":252934,"text":"is it's not that hard\nto make these things."},{"time":255103,"text":"The equipment you need\ncan be built from garbage,"},{"time":258059,"text":"and the key processing step\nonly requires soap and water."},{"time":262866,"text":"So what we did was put all\nthe instructions online as open source."},{"time":267393,"text":"And then we founded\na mission-driven company,"},{"time":269553,"text":"and we're developing kits\nto make it easier"},{"time":271955,"text":"for anyone with a sink\nand a soldering iron"},{"time":274550,"text":"to make these things at home."},{"time":276132,"text":"What I'm really curious\nabout is if one day,"},{"time":280229,"text":"it will be possible to repair, rebuild\nand augment our own bodies"},{"time":285504,"text":"with stuff we make in the kitchen."}]},{"cues":[{"time":289321,"text":"Speaking of kitchens,"},{"time":291442,"text":"here's some asparagus."},{"time":293402,"text":"They're tasty, and they make\nyour pee smell funny."}]},{"cues":[{"time":296109,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":297386,"text":"Now, I was in my kitchen,\nand I was noticing"},{"time":300033,"text":"that when you look down\nthe stalks of these asparagus,"},{"time":302643,"text":"what you can see\nare all these tiny little vessels."},{"time":305658,"text":"And when we image them in the lab,"},{"time":307331,"text":"you can see how the cellulose\nforms these structures."},{"time":310832,"text":"This image reminds me of two things:"},{"time":313701,"text":"our blood vessels"},{"time":315607,"text":"and the structure and organization\nof our nerves and spinal cord."}]},{"cues":[{"time":319854,"text":"So here's the question:"},{"time":321860,"text":"Can we grow axons and neurons\ndown these channels?"},{"time":326064,"text":"Because if we can,"},{"time":327714,"text":"then maybe we can use asparagus\nto form new connections"},{"time":332005,"text":"between the ends of damaged\nand severed nerves."},{"time":335627,"text":"Or maybe even a spinal cord."},{"time":338126,"text":"Don't get me wrong --"},{"time":339436,"text":"this is exceptionally challenging"},{"time":341464,"text":"and really hard work to do,"},{"time":343083,"text":"and we are not the only ones\nworking on this."},{"time":346116,"text":"But we are the only ones using asparagus."}]},{"cues":[{"time":349080,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":352060,"text":"Right now, we've got\nreally promising pilot data."},{"time":355202,"text":"And we're working with tissue engineers"},{"time":357109,"text":"and neurosurgeons"},{"time":358299,"text":"to find out what's actually possible."}]},{"cues":[{"time":360793,"text":"So listen, all of the work I've shown you,"},{"time":363371,"text":"the stuff that I've built\nthat's all around me on this stage"},{"time":366588,"text":"and the other projects\nmy lab is involved in"},{"time":369282,"text":"are all a direct result\nof me playing with your garbage."},{"time":373393,"text":"Play -- play is a key part\nof my scientific practice."},{"time":379454,"text":"It's how I train my mind\nto be unconventional and to be creative"},{"time":383462,"text":"and to decide to make human apple ears."}]},{"cues":[{"time":386491,"text":"So, the next time any of you\nare looking at some old,"},{"time":391166,"text":"broken-down, malfunctioning,\npiece-of-crap technology,"},{"time":395769,"text":"I want you to think of me."},{"time":398199,"text":"Because I want it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":399381,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":400556,"text":"Seriously, please find any way\nto get in touch with me,"},{"time":404587,"text":"and let's see what we can build."}]},{"cues":[{"time":406552,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":407727,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}